CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 11, 1959, pg. 21, reads: "At New Diamond Market - Above is part of the crowd which visited the New Diamond Market's grand opening at its produce and fruit department last Saturday.  The market is located at 211 Forbes St., and offers some of the best bargains in the city week after week. - Harris Photo. - Adv."
TitMainTitle: Women and men in New Diamond Market grocery store with large display of bananas, and man behind produce counter wearing apron and striped shirt, Downtown
